}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== From a sample card with no S/N (worn off) or visible version info... *The card label states it was made in Taiwan. *The card's OUI is 00:10:7A ('''[[AmbiCom]]'''). *The card's PCI ID is 1011:0019 (<small>'''Digital Equipment Corporation''' DECchip 21142/43</small>), SS: 1385:2100 The dongle is labeled with... *top - the '''[[NETGEAR]]''' logo and separate media speed LED indicators *bottom - "FA510 Media Coupler" and "ACC-035-011" on a label
The copyright year of '''[[NETGEAR]]''''s manual is 2000.
==Links of Interest== {{SupportPage|vendor=NETGEAR|model = FA510}} (card has long since EoL, though the manual and drivers are still available ATM)
